At European level:&#xd;
ALFI is an active member of EFAMA (European Fund and Asset Management Association) where it is represented in all major technical committees and working groups and contributes to ongoing works of the association.&#xd;
ALFI has been a member of Pensions Europe since 2011.&#xd;
&#xd;
At International level:&#xd;
ALFI is a member of the International Investment Funds Association (IIFA).&#xd;
&#xd;
At national level:&#xd;
ALFI is a member of associations / chambers of commerce like AmCham, British Chamber of Commerce, Italian Chamber of Commerce, Chilean Chamber of Commerce, Indian Chamber of Commerce, ...
